🍔 Burger Shop Application

A Java Swing-based desktop application that simulates a simple Burger Shop system.
Built with NetBeans IDE and Java Swing GUI, this project demonstrates fundamental software engineering concepts such as GUI design, event handling, object-oriented programming specially the importance of encapsulation, and user interaction.

✨ Features

🖥️ GUI Interface using Java Swing

🍔 Add burgers

🧾 Place and manage customer orders

💵 Bill calculation with order summary

📊 Display best customers / order history (if included)

🔄 Clear / reset orders

🛠️ Technologies Used

Java (JDK 17 or above recommended)

Swing (Java GUI framework)

NetBeans IDE

🚀 How to Run

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/YasiruPerera001/BurgerShopApplication.git


Open the project in NetBeans IDE (or any Java IDE).

Build & Run the project.

